706769f-a.title: Brooklyn: Shore Road - 72nd Street
706769f-a.text:
Shore Road, north from 7end Street. One of many apartments erected in
this area. It is one of the finest residential places in this Borough.
June S, 1931.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.

706770f-a.title: Brooklyn: Shore Road - 72nd Street
706770f-a.text:
Shore Road, east side, south of 72nd Street, showing a building on land
which at one time belonged to John L. Bennett.
1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
